<noinclude>
==Documentation==
Renders the concept page sidebar with structured data pulled from Semantic MediaWiki properties.

This template is called automatically by <code><nowiki>{{ConceptEnd}}</nowiki></code>.

===Sections===
# '''Concept details''' - Name, game count, aliases
# '''Related content''' - Accordion sections for Games, Franchises, Characters, Locations, Objects, People, Related Concepts

===SMW Properties Used===
* <code>Has name</code> - Concept name
* <code>Has aliases</code> - Alternative names
* <code>Has games</code> - Games featuring this concept
* <code>Has franchises</code> - Franchises with this concept
* <code>Has characters</code> - Associated characters
* <code>Has locations</code> - Associated locations
* <code>Has objects</code> - Associated objects
* <code>Has people</code> - Associated people
* <code>Has related concepts</code> - Similar/related concepts
</noinclude><includeonly>
